Package edu.sru.thangiah.datastructures.generic.linkedlist

Class SingleLinkedListGeneric<T extends Comparable<T>>

java.lang.Object
edu.sru.thangiah.datastructures.generic.linkedlist.AbstractSingleLinkedListGeneric<T>
edu.sru.thangiah.datastructures.generic.linkedlist.SingleLinkedListGeneric<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
BaseOpsGeneric<T>, ListOpsGeneric<T>
public class SingleLinkedListGeneric<T extends Comparable<T>> extends AbstractSingleLinkedListGeneric<T>

Title: SingleLinkedListGeneric

Description:

BaseOps interface class Single linked list generic implementation. Users can call linked list specific methods (insert, add, remove, getAtIndex, etc.) and also create instances of a linked list with any data type.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Sam R. Thangiah
